/* Table: "MD_Brand" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "MD_Brand"
(
"BrandID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"REMBrandGUID" VARCHAR2(100),
"BrandCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"BrandName" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"PinYinSpell" VARCHAR2(500),
"Remark" NVARCHAR2(500),
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
REMGUID VARCHAR2(100),
constraint PK_MD_BRAND primary key ("BrandID")
)
/

comment on column "MD_Brand"."Enable" is
'1: 有效
0：无效'
